& [UnrealPlatformWorkSliceIndex] is the project-manager index for the UE5 Roblox-like platform work
  + [index_uuid] is b970bc3a-9499-4553-bdaa-66179389f95e
  + [project_subject] is UE5-powered user-generated multiplayer game platform
  + [source_document] is unreal_platform_project/source_documents/2026-06-21_platform_intake/Dictated_Unreal_Platform_Source.sop
  + [feature_import_specification] is unreal_platform_project/specifications/Roblox_Feature_Import_Specification.sop
  + [active_feature_specification] is unreal_platform_project/specifications/Multiplayer_Splitscreen_Hosting_Feature_Specification.sop
  + [active_data_contract] is unreal_platform_project/specifications/contracts/Multiplayer_Splitscreen_Data_Contracts.sop
  + [coordination_mode] is single_conversation_project_manager
  + [coordination_layer] is inactive
  + [manager_rule] is complete and review one slice before claiming the next dependent slice

  & [ReadinessModel] is the local status vocabulary
    + [ready] is clear enough for immediate work
    + [blocked] is waiting on dependency or unresolved decision
    + [deferred] is valid future work outside the current frontier
    + [active] is currently being prepared or reviewed
    + [complete] is finished and reviewed for support_delta and requirement_delta

  & [SliceSet] is the ordered work map
    + [slice_01] is unreal_platform_project/planning/project_manager/slices/Slice_01_Multiplayer_Splitscreen_Data_Contract.sop
      + [status] is complete
      + [depends_on] is source preservation and feature expansion draft
      + [completion_review] is unreal_platform_project/planning/project_manager/reviews/Review_2026-06-21_Multiplayer_Splitscreen_Scaffold.sop
    + [slice_02] is unreal_platform_project/planning/project_manager/slices/Slice_02_UE5_Prototype_Host_Session_Scaffold.sop
      + [status] is complete
      + [depends_on] is slice_01 review
      + [completion_review] is unreal_platform_project/planning/project_manager/reviews/Review_2026-06-21_Multiplayer_Splitscreen_Scaffold.sop
    + [slice_03] is future slice for mock authentication and user-slot binding
      + [status] is ready
      + [depends_on] is slice_02
    + [slice_04] is future slice for split-screen player creation, input isolation, and HUD proof
      + [status] is deferred
      + [depends_on] is slice_03
    + [slice_05] is future slice for audit log persistence and smoke proof
      + [status] is deferred
      + [depends_on] is slice_04

  & [ManagerNextFrontier] is the recommended immediate work order
    + [first] is implement two-player local split-screen slot creation using the compiled host-session scaffold
    + [second] is add HUD proof that distinct mock users are bound to distinct local slots
    + [third] is add smoke proof for audit events and identity-collapse guard

  & [CompletedWorkReviewRule] is the manager check between slices
    = must: inspect completed slice deliverables
    = must: record support_delta when a slice supports another requirement
    = must: record requirement_delta when a slice changes the requirement shape
    = must: update this index before starting a dependent slice
    - never: proceed from a completed slice as if completion is only a stamp
